    <title>《极限竞速：地平线 4》达史低</title>
    <url>/2024/12/05/%E3%80%8A%E6%9E%81%E9%99%90%E7%AB%9E%E9%80%9F%EF%BC%9A%E5%9C%B0%E5%B9%B3%E7%BA%BF%204%E3%80%8B%E8%BE%BE%E5%8F%B2%E4%BD%8E/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="极限竞速：地平线-4"><a href="#极限竞速：地平线-4" class="headerlink" title="极限竞速：地平线 4"></a>极限竞速：地平线 4</h1><h2 id="折扣平台"><a href="#折扣平台" class="headerlink" title="折扣平台"></a>折扣平台</h2><a class="button " href='https://store.steampowered.com/app/1293830/' title='Steam'><i class='fa-brands fa-steam'></i> Steam</a>
<h2 id="折扣价格"><a href="#折扣价格" class="headerlink" title="折扣价格"></a>折扣价格</h2><p>（<del>新史低价格将<strong>加粗</strong>显示</del>）此次折扣仅达史低，详情请查看<a class="link"   href="https://steamdb.info/app/1293830/" >SteamDB</a></p>
<ul>
<li>原价：￥188.00（-0%）</li>
<li>史低：￥37.60（-80%）</li>
